2014;;Snow in Paradise;;British;;Director: Andrew Hulme;;Director: Andrew HulmeCast: Frederick Schmidt, Martin Askew, David Spinx;;unknown;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Snow_in_Paradise;;Petty criminal Dave lives in London, high on crime and drugs. After a heist gone wrong brings about his best friend's death, he turns to Islam for finding peace to his feelings for shame and remorse, but soon his past life comes back to haunt him.